# Local build artifacts (binaries are produced by CI; never committed).
# Anchor with leading slash — without it, gitignore matches the
# substring `geyserlite` anywhere in the tree, including the Java
# package path com/minekube/geyserlite/, which silently dropped
# GeyserBridge*.java on every checkout. THE BRIDGE WAS NEVER COMMITTED
# until 2026-05-03 because of this.
/geyserlite
libgeyserlite.so
libgeyserlite.h
*.iprof

# Per-target embed assets (downloaded by `task embed:fetch`, never committed).
# README.md inside these dirs IS committed.
go/assets/*
!go/assets/README.md
rust/assets/*
!rust/assets/README.md

# Fetched Geyser source tree during local builds
build/.work/
build/Geyser/

# Floodgate keys / secrets — never committed
floodgate.pem
floodgate.key
*.pem
!build/overlay/**/*.pem

# Local mise/cargo/go caches (kept inside the repo via mise.toml [env])
.cache/

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp

# Go
**/vendor
/bin

# Rust
target/
Cargo.lock
!rust/Cargo.lock
